Q: Jane is celebrating the last day of Jan 2012. What is the date a month ago in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If today is the last day of Jan 2012, then today is 01/31/2012. A month ago from today is 1 month in the past of today, which is the 31st day of December 2011, or 12/31/2011. So the answer is 12/31/2011.

